text: @FedExHelp why doesn’t a local FedEx kinkos office accept a package that’s in a shoebox but the drivers will?

@rdifrango @rdifrango Hello, this is Joe. I do apologize on behalf of Fedex about your shipment issue. According to the Fedex service guide, packages for shipment should be in customer's own customized packaging or in official Fedex packaging. 
https://t.co/LLQt3HKBO8
Thank you.
~joe
